{"id":232665429,"title":"綠色聖誕禮物建議","content":"最近收到王道銀行的EDM是關於綠色消費的宣傳\n只要持卡到合作的20幾家綠色品牌消費 都有額外4.22%的回饋\n\n說實在的從之前他們表態力挺彩虹到前陣子的喜憨兒聯名卡\n一直覺得這間銀行在社會議題還算滿用心經營的\n剛好聖誕節想挑一個對環境或是社會友善的禮物送我姊\n就順便貼出來給大家參考囉 \nhttp://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQ.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/kWvpvQR.png\n我自己目前是偏好 綠藤 繭裹子 或 茶籽堂\n綠藤生機：我自己是有用辣木油跟洗髮精\n繭果子：洋裝或外套都很生火，但價格也比較小貴一點\n茶籽堂：最近苦茶油很夯，但我姊好像也很少煮飯，考慮考慮\n\n不知道大家有推薦，適合當禮物的嗎？","excerpt":"最近收到王道銀行的EDM是關於綠色消費的宣傳，只要持卡到合作的20幾家綠色品牌消費 都有額外4.22%的回饋，說實在的從之前他們表態力挺彩虹到前陣子的喜憨兒聯名卡，一直覺得這間銀行在社會議題還算滿用心","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":25,"tags":[],"topics":["禮物","環保","綠色","愛地球"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"致理科技大學","department":"國際貿易系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":25}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQ.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/kWvpvQR.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9612d876-f52d-4c16-a771-886814d43236","url":"https://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z"},{"id":"9612d876-f52d-4c16-a771-886814d43236","url":"http://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQ.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/DfyDYOQ","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DfyDYOQl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T06:42:37.338Z"},{"id":"25e65752-a64c-4b7c-ab7c-089627cb09fe"